column6: THE SHOCKING CONCLUSION! - The climactic, life changing conclusion for the rawest, grittiest new team on the block. Their fate hangs in the balance! - Can THE ULTIMATES save the city from catastrophe yet again and survive the process? - Monsters, mayhem, and super powered fisticuffs! If this isn't the MARVEL COMIC TO END ALL MARVEL COMICS, we don't know what is!
column8: | writer:Michel Fiffe | penciller (cover):David Nakayama | artist:Amilcar Pinna
